<style>
  .clara-docs {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 0 40px;
    color: #111827;
  }

  .clara-docs h1 {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 4px;
  }

  .clara-docs h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 24px 0 4px;
  }

  .clara-docs h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 16px 0 4px;
  }

  .clara-docs p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 4px 0 10px;
  }

  .clara-docs ul {
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 4px 0 20px 18px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .clara-docs li {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .clara-docs hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .clara-docs a {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .clara-docs a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .clara-docs-lead {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-top: 4px;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .clara-prompt-box {
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    background: var(--slate-50);
    padding: 8px 10px;
    margin: 8px 0;
  }

  .clara-prompt-box-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .clara-prompt-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .clara-prompt-cta {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: #4f46e5;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
    background: var(--slate-200);
    padding: 0px 6px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .clara-prompt-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    color: #111827;
  }

  /* Make examples feel like clickable buttons */
  .clara-prompt-box--clickable {
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.12s ease, transform 0.08s ease;
  }

  .clara-prompt-box--clickable:hover {
    background: var(--slate-100);
    box-shadow: 0px 5px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .clara-prompt-box--clickable:active {
    transform: translateY(0);
    box-shadow: 0px 5px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
</style>

<div class="clara-docs">
  <h1>CLARA Docs</h1><h3><%= @version %></h3>
  <p class="clara-docs-lead">
    Clara is your culture copilot. Ask questions in plain language and it will pull your live data,
    explain what it means, and suggest what to do next.
  </p>

  <hr>

  <h2>Start here</h2>
  <p>
    New to Clara? Try these to get a quick, useful read on what’s happening right now.
  </p>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Give me a simple culture pulse for the last 30 days. What’s healthy, what’s risky, and what changed most?">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Quick pulse check</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Give me a simple culture pulse for the last 30 days. What’s healthy, what’s risky, and what changed most?”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Summarize the last 30 days across Employee Engagement, Alignment, Psychological Safety, Execution Risk, Conflict, and Burnout in 6 bullet points.">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Executive summary</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Summarize the last 30 days across Employee Engagement, Alignment, Psychological Safety, Execution Risk, Conflict, and Burnout in 6 bullet points.”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Which teams improved the most in the last 30 days, and what do they have in common?">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Biggest wins</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Which teams improved the most in the last 30 days, and what do they have in common?”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="What should I be paying attention to this week based on the most recent signals?">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">What matters now</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“What should I be paying attention to this week based on the most recent signals?”    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2>Go deeper</h2>
  <p>
    Use these when something looks off and you want the “why,” not just the score.
  </p>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Do a deep dive on Burnout for the last 45 days. Which submetrics are in the worst shape, and which signals are driving them?">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Root-cause the issue</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Do a deep dive on Burnout for the last 45 days. Which submetrics are in the worst shape, and which signals are driving them?”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Explain what’s behind the recent dip in Psychological Safety. Use the top 5 negative signals and translate them into plain language.">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Translate signals</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Explain what’s behind the recent dip in Psychological Safety. Use the top 5 negative signals and translate them into plain language.”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Show how Engagement and Burnout moved together over the last 90 days. Are they linked, or drifting apart?">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Connect the dots</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Show how Engagement and Burnout moved together over the last 90 days. Are they linked, or drifting apart?”    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2>Compare & contrast</h2>
  <p>
    Great for spotting gaps between teams, leaders, or time periods.
  </p>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Compare Psychological Safety for leaders vs frontline teams over the last 60 days. How big is the gap and is it widening?">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Leaders vs teams</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Compare Psychological Safety for leaders vs frontline teams over the last 60 days. How big is the gap and is it widening?”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Which groups are the biggest outliers for Conflict in the last 30 days? Summarize the top 5 and the themes you see.">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Find outliers</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Which groups are the biggest outliers for Conflict in the last 30 days? Summarize the top 5 and the themes you see.”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="We launched a new meeting policy on March 1. Compare Burnout and Engagement 14 days before vs 14 days after that date and explain what changed.">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Before / after event</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“We launched a new meeting policy on March 1. Compare Burnout and Engagement 14 days before vs 14 days after that date and explain what changed.”    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2>Get recommendations</h2>
  <p>
    When you’re ready to act, ask Clara for focused, practical next steps.
  </p>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Based on the last 60 days of Burnout and Psychological Safety, give me 3 specific actions we should take in the next 30 days.">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Short action list</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Based on the last 60 days of Burnout and Psychological Safety, give me 3 specific actions we should take in the next 30 days.”    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Conflict is high in Customer Success. Using our data and playbooks, outline a 30-day plan to reduce conflict and rebuild trust.">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Team intervention plan</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Conflict is high in Customer Success. Using our data and playbooks, outline a 30-day plan to reduce conflict and rebuild trust.”    </div>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2>Pro tips</h2>
  <p>
    The best answers come from clear questions. Be specific about time range, metric, and group — and ask for the format you want.
  </p>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Rewrite my question to get a clearer answer: “Are we okay?”">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Level up the question</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Rewrite my question to get a clearer answer: “Are we okay?””    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clara-prompt-box clara-prompt-box--clickable"
       role="button" tabindex="0"
       data-clara-prompt="Give me a template I can reuse for asking about any metric (time window, group, comparison, and a clear output format).">
    <div class="clara-prompt-box-header">
      <div class="clara-prompt-label">Reusable prompt template</div>
      <div class="clara-prompt-cta">Click to try →</div>
    </div>
    <div class="clara-prompt-text">
“Give me a template I can reuse for asking about any metric (time window, group, comparison, and a clear output format).”    </div>
  </div>
</div>
